This is a great way to "look" at all the constellations based on your location.  The vivid pictures and colors look great on my HTC phone.  Not only did I find that I could look up all the constellations, but also planets, moons, showers and more.  It can be tough to research these things without a device on hand unless you are a "master astrologer," but luckily I found that using the app is an easy way to track everything better than Neil Degrasse Tyson!  Love this app and I highly recommend it!

Cool astronomy app with accurate mapping. I'm going camping for the memorial day holiday and wanted to surprise and impress my family with my new astronomy knowledge. It gives information based on personal coordinates through GPS. The ability to search by name and constellation makes it easier to use. I've memorized 4 constellations so far. I love my new hobby.
